name: THE SUN -  4/4 MAJOR ARCANA
description:
XIX  EL SOL

The last of my Major Arcana HENesis collection. It started with death, and the end is just another sunrise. Death and dawn can be either beginnings or endings, and in between, time goes by. 

 - In 2019 I created my first tarot deck: El Tarot de la Fuerza, this collection of MAJOR ARCANA is part of its second edition -
